item.title: t-amp reboxing part 1 of 1
item.description: Tonight ruled. while waiting for the graffiti artist to work and finish and such i decided to do my t-amp project. i got all the rest of my parts i ordered to rebox the sonic impact t-amp. i followed the directions and parts lists from this awesome site. it was quite quite helpful. I have found a LOT of sites dealing with the t-amp and that one is quite possibly the most complete.
